article.headline: Stephen F. Austin 94, Centenary 57
article.story: NACOGDOCHES, Texas (AP) -- Five players scored in double digits, led by Josh Alexander's 18 points, as Stephen F. Austin beat Centenary 94-57 on Saturday night. Chaz Dykes scored 16 points, Matt Kingsley had 11, Marcus Clark scored 12 and Antuane Miller added 10 for Stephen F. Austin (5-2). Xavier Burnette had 13 points to lead Centenary (1-5). Centenary shot 38.8 percent for the game.
